As the user <%= @user.first_name %>, I want to see my recommanded projects:
<p>Name of the projet: <%= @project.name %></p>

<form action="/users/<%= @user.id %>/donations" method="post">
  <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>
  <input name="project_id" type="hidden" value="<%= @project.id %>">
  <input type="submit" value="Make a donation">
</form>
